0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:52:09.000Z","msg":"818！！！"},{"pid":"72e33acf98a3e0116f9858375c4185db689400dc","tid":1469170,"uid":189799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:09:52.000Z","msg":"發夢食過幾次催淚彈。<br />\n 其實次次都傷唔到黑警，前期一放催淚彈就散。到宜家有滅火隊，黑警一衝，我地都係散。<br />\n<br />\n 唔係話勇武派無用，勇武派嘅作用唔係要傷到黑警，而係令黑警做不合理嘅事。<br />\n<br />\n 例如<br />\n 612嘅過份武力，令政府停止修例<br />\n 各區放催淚彈，亂拉街坊，打頭<br />\n 811 射眼<br />\n<br />\n 每件事都係用前線嘅血換番黎。落力宣傳先對得住受傷嘅前線。所以不如咁玩<br />\n<br />\n 勇武＞黑警射眼＞宣傳黑警射眼＞勇武<br />\n<br />\n 818全民紗布遮眼遊行，之後散水瞓教。少1日勇武，換黎嘅係819各傳媒集中報道遮眼遊行，個個人都知黑警射盲左一個女仔集眼。<br />\n<br />\n唔想個女仔白白無左隻眼"},{"pid":"7b8e57fb5ab3753c305bf39417c15d40a73b6f8f","tid":1469170,"uid":244332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f0810b2a12409275b74605b13a039469486a42ba","tid":1469170,"uid":20834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:52:09.000Z","msg":"818！！！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:32:43.000Z","msg":"全力宣傳818<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afcc720f90c60fadb11f76df788204cde9d4d45c","tid":1469170,"uid":244332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:37:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91eb2e17ee2273d0d7a56519ea602d9f6e88c9ea","tid":1469170,"uid":244332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T09:43:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3230e2cfdc2c68aa92cd657ea84b65896aaeae6b","tid":1469170,"uid":295218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T09:47:53.000Z","msg":"我班連登仔，我係鬼都忍唔住岀嚟笑柒你<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1470387\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1470387</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f6b45e4cddca08ee731f86755487b58aaa48ae14","tid":1469170,"uid":14244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T09:48:55.000Z","msg":"818 全人